<F P=100> WEST EUROPE </F>
<F P=101> DENMARK </F>
<H3> <TI>   Energy Minister: Environment Top Priority in Energy Policy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Energy Minister: Environment Top Priority in Energy Policy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WN0265A Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE in Danish 19 Apr 94 
p III 4 </F>

