<H3> <TI>   New Dioxin Hazard Said `Threatening' Germany </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Dioxin Hazard Said `Threatening' Germany </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1905081494 Bonn DIE WELT in German 22 Apr 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> BR1905081494 </F>
<F P=104>  Bonn DIE WELT </F>
