<F P=106> [SDA report: "3,511 AIDS Cases in Switzerland"] </F>
  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] So far, 3,511 AIDS cases have 
been registered in Switzerland and 2,418 of the infected persons 
have died of the AIDS virus. Last year alone, 634 new cases 
were registered. Drug addicts and homosexual and bisexual men 
are still affected most. Regarding the spread in the cantons, 
the largest number of sick persons is to be found in Zurich with 
1,268 cases, followed by Geneva with 521 cases, and Waadt with 
421 cases. 

