<H3> <TI>   Epidemiological Reports Monitored 4-10 April </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Epidemiological Reports Monitored 4-10 April </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MB1004175394 </F>
