<H4>    Blix Meets Amrollahi </H4>

<F P=102> LD1804144994 Tehran IRNA in English 1439 GMT 18 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1804144994 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tehran, April 18, IRNA -- Head of Iran's Atomic 
Energy Organization, Reza Amrollahi, and secretary general of 
the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA), Hans Blix, 
discussed declaring the Middle East region a nuclear free zone 
(NFZ) Monday. 
  At the meeting Blix welcomed Iran's proposal on promoting 
technical cooperation between Iran and IAEA. 
  Blix arrived here Monday morning to hold talks with Iranian 
officials on joint cooperation. 
  During his two day stay here Blix is expected to hold 
discussions with senior Iranian officials. 

</TEXT>

