<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On 15 April the press center of the Security Service 
of Ukraine reported that Swedish subject Erik Olaf Estenson, 
born in 1962, who was temporarily staying on the territory of 
our state, was expelled from Ukraine for attempts to carry out 
actions which can be qualified as international nuclear 
